    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "え……？　休暇ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Day off?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、東京に移転してからもみんな頑張って\nくれたからな。たまにはゆっくりしてほしいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Everyone has been working so hard since we moved to Tokyo.\nA break every now and then is good for everybody.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.633333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリに勝ってから\n一気にオファーが増えましたからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true that we’ve been getting a lot of offers\nsince we won the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "メディアの露出も増えて、最近忙しいですから\n休みをもらえるのは嬉しいんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With all the media sessions and work‚\nI guess a day off isn’t such a bad idea…but",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いつもより歯切れが悪いな……\n何か不安でもあるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You sound a little unsure.\nAre you worried about something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "……言いにくいんですけど、その\n……実は最近、自分のダンスに自信が持てないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… it’s not easy to say out loud‚ but…\nLately‚ I haven’t felt confident about my own dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}